# 📖 Dokumentasi Backend Bizkit POS

## 1. Struktur Folder

```
bizkit-api/
├── .env                  ← Konfigurasi environment
├── main.go               ← Entry point: inisialisasi server + semua routes
├── go.mod / go.sum       ← Dependency management
│
├── config/
│   └── database.go       ← Koneksi MySQL + AutoMigrate + Seeder
│
├── models/               ← Semua struct database (GORM)
│   ├── user.go           ← Role, Outlet, User
│   ├── inventory.go      ← Category, Brand, Unit, Product, Variant, VariantOption, PriceCategory
│   ├── order.go          ← PaymentMethod, Order, OrderItem
│   ├── promotion.go      ← Promotion
│   ├── shift.go          ← Shift
│   └── attendance.go     ← Attendance
│
├── controllers/          ← Handler untuk setiap API endpoint
│   ├── auth_controller.go
│   ├── category_controller.go
│   ├── brand_controller.go
│   ├── unit_controller.go
│   ├── product_controller.go
│   ├── variant_controller.go
│   ├── price_category_controller.go
│   ├── payment_method_controller.go
│   ├── user_controller.go
│   ├── promotion_controller.go
│   ├── shift_controller.go
│   ├── attendance_controller.go
│   └── report_controller.go
│
├── middleware/
│   └── auth.go           ← JWT AuthMiddleware + RoleMiddleware
│
├── dtos/
│   └── auth_dto.go       ← LoginRequest / LoginResponse struct
│
└── utils/
    └── jwt.go            ← Generate & Validate JWT token
```

---

## 2. Alur Kerja Aplikasi (Request Flow)

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant FE as Frontend (React)
    participant GIN as Gin Router
    participant MW as AuthMiddleware
    participant CTRL as Controller
    participant DB as MySQL (GORM)

    Note over FE,DB: 🔓 Login (tanpa middleware)
    FE->>GIN: POST /api/auth/login {username, password}
    GIN->>CTRL: auth_controller.Login()
    CTRL->>DB: Cari user by username + Preload Role & Outlet
    DB-->>CTRL: User data
    CTRL->>CTRL: Verify password (bcrypt)
    CTRL->>CTRL: Generate JWT token (24 jam)
    CTRL-->>FE: {token, user: {id, username, role, outlet_name}}

    Note over FE,DB: 🔒 Protected API (dengan middleware)
    FE->>GIN: GET /api/master/products (Header: Bearer token)
    GIN->>MW: AuthMiddleware() → validasi JWT
    MW->>MW: Parse token → extract userID, username, role
    MW->>GIN: Set context: userID, username, role
    GIN->>CTRL: product_controller.GetProducts()
    CTRL->>DB: Preload Category, Brand, Unit → Find all
    DB-->>CTRL: Products data
    CTRL-->>FE: {data: [...products]}
```

---

