## 4. Penjelasan Relasi Database

### 👤 User & Akses

| Relasi | Penjelasan |
|--------|-----------|
| **Role → User** | Satu role (Owner/Admin/Kasir) bisa punya banyak user |
| **Outlet → User** | Satu outlet bisa punya banyak user (karyawan) |
| **User → Order** | Satu user (kasir) bisa membuat banyak order |
| **User → Shift** | Satu user punya banyak catatan pergantian shift |
| **User → Attendance** | Satu user punya banyak catatan absensi |

### 📦 Produk & Inventaris

| Relasi | Penjelasan |
|--------|-----------|
| **Category → Product** | Satu kategori (Makanan/Minuman) punya banyak produk |
| **Brand → Product** | Satu merek (Dagashi) punya banyak produk |
| **Unit → Product** | Satu satuan (Pcs/Porsi) dipakai banyak produk |
| **Variant → VariantOption** | Satu varian (Level Pedas) punya banyak opsi (Pedas/Sedang/Mild) |

### 🛒 Transaksi

| Relasi | Penjelasan |
|--------|-----------|
| **Order → OrderItem** | Satu order punya banyak item belanjaan |
| **Product → OrderItem** | Satu produk bisa muncul di banyak order item |
| **PaymentMethod → Order** | Satu metode bayar (Tunai/QRIS) dipakai banyak order |
| **Outlet → Order** | Satu outlet punya banyak order |

### 🏷️ Standalone (tanpa relasi FK)

| Entity | Penjelasan |
|--------|-----------|
| **PriceCategory** | Kategori harga tambahan (Gojek/Grab), data master mandiri |
| **Promotion** | Promo & voucher, data mandiri (belum terhubung ke order) |

---

## 5. Fitur Khusus GORM

### 🗑️ Soft Delete
Semua entity punya field `DeletedAt gorm.DeletedAt`. Artinya:
- `DELETE` **tidak menghapus** data dari database
- Hanya mengisi kolom `deleted_at` dengan timestamp
- Query `Find()` otomatis meng-exclude data yang sudah di-delete
- Data bisa di-recover jika diperlukan

### 🔗 Preload (Eager Loading)
```go
// Contoh: ambil products beserta relasi-nya
config.DB.Preload("Category").Preload("Brand").Preload("Unit").Find(&products)
```
Ini akan menjalankan 4 query SQL:
1. `SELECT * FROM products WHERE deleted_at IS NULL`
2. `SELECT * FROM categories WHERE id IN (...)`
3. `SELECT * FROM brands WHERE id IN (...)`
4. `SELECT * FROM units WHERE id IN (...)`

### 🔄 AutoMigrate
```go
database.AutoMigrate(&models.Role{}, &models.Product{}, ...)
```
- Otomatis membuat tabel jika belum ada
- Otomatis menambah kolom baru jika ada field baru di struct
- **Tidak akan menghapus** kolom yang sudah ada

---

## 6. Authentication Flow

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    A["POST /api/auth/login\n{username, password}"] --> B{User ditemukan?}
    B -->|Tidak| C["401: Invalid username or password"]
    B -->|Ya| D{Password cocok?\nbcrypt.Compare}
    D -->|Tidak| C
    D -->|Ya| E["Generate JWT Token\n(berlaku 24 jam)"]
    E --> F["Response:\n{token, user}"]

    G["Request API lain\nHeader: Bearer TOKEN"] --> H["AuthMiddleware"]
    H --> I{Token valid?}
    I -->|Tidak| J["401: Invalid token"]
    I -->|Ya| K["Set context:\nuserID, username, role"]
    K --> L["Controller dijalankan"]
```

**JWT Payload (Claims):**
```json
{
  "user_id": 1,
  "username": "ownerdemo",
  "role": "Owner",
  "exp": 1741200000
}
```

---

## 7. API Reference (46 Endpoints)

### 🔓 Auth (tanpa token)

| Method | Path | Body | Response |
|--------|------|------|----------|
| POST | `/api/auth/login` | `{username, password}` | `{token, user: {id, username, role, outlet_name}}` |

### 📦 Master Data (perlu token)

| Resource | GET (list) | POST (create) | PUT (update) | DELETE |
|----------|-----------|---------------|-------------|--------|
| Categories | `/api/master/categories` | ← `{name}` | [/:id](file:///d:/laragon/www/belajar/bizkit/bizkit-web/src/components/Layout.jsx#56-72) `{name}` | [/:id](file:///d:/laragon/www/belajar/bizkit/bizkit-web/src/components/Layout.jsx#56-72) |
| Brands | `/api/master/brands` | ← `{name}` | [/:id](file:///d:/laragon/www/belajar/bizkit/bizkit-web/src/components/Layout.jsx#56-72) `{name}` | [/:id](file:///d:/laragon/www/belajar/bizkit/bizkit-web/src/components/Layout.jsx#56-72) |
| Units | `/api/master/units` | ← `{name}` | [/:id](file:///d:/laragon/www/belajar/bizkit/bizkit-web/src/components/Layout.jsx#56-72) `{name}` | [/:id](file:///d:/laragon/www/belajar/bizkit/bizkit-web/src/components/Layout.jsx#56-72) |
| Products | `/api/master/products` | ← `{name, category_id, brand_id, unit_id, price, status?}` | [/:id](file:///d:/laragon/www/belajar/bizkit/bizkit-web/src/components/Layout.jsx#56-72) | [/:id](file:///d:/laragon/www/belajar/bizkit/bizkit-web/src/components/Layout.jsx#56-72) |
| Variants | `/api/master/variants` | ← `{name, description?, min_choice?, max_choice?, status?}` | [/:id](file:///d:/laragon/www/belajar/bizkit/bizkit-web/src/components/Layout.jsx#56-72) | [/:id](file:///d:/laragon/www/belajar/bizkit/bizkit-web/src/components/Layout.jsx#56-72) |
| Price Categories | `/api/master/price-categories` | ← `{name}` | [/:id](file:///d:/laragon/www/belajar/bizkit/bizkit-web/src/components/Layout.jsx#56-72) `{name}` | [/:id](file:///d:/laragon/www/belajar/bizkit/bizkit-web/src/components/Layout.jsx#56-72) |
| Payment Methods | `/api/master/payment-methods` | ← `{name, status?}` | [/:id](file:///d:/laragon/www/belajar/bizkit/bizkit-web/src/components/Layout.jsx#56-72) `{name, status}` | [/:id](file:///d:/laragon/www/belajar/bizkit/bizkit-web/src/components/Layout.jsx#56-72) |

### 👤 Users (perlu token)

| Method | Path | Body |
|--------|------|------|
| GET | `/api/users` | — |
| POST | `/api/users` | `{username, password, role_id, outlet_id}` |
| PUT | `/api/users/:id` | `{username?, role_id?, outlet_id?}` |
| DELETE | `/api/users/:id` | — |
| PUT | `/api/users/:id/reset-password` | `{password}` |

### 🏷️ Promotions (perlu token)

| Method | Path | Body |
|--------|------|------|
| GET | `/api/promotions` | — |
| POST | `/api/promotions` | `{name, type?, start_date, end_date, max_usage?, days?, conditions?, status?}` |
| PUT | `/api/promotions/:id` | Partial update |
| DELETE | `/api/promotions/:id` | — |

### ⏱️ Shifts (perlu token)

| Method | Path | Body / Query |
|--------|------|-------------|
| GET | `/api/shifts?start_date=&end_date=` | Filter by date range |
| POST | `/api/shifts` | `{user_id, description?, type, amount_in?, amount_out?, balance?}` |

### 📋 Attendances (perlu token)

| Method | Path | Body / Query |
|--------|------|-------------|
| GET | `/api/attendances?date=YYYY-MM-DD` | Filter by date |
| POST | `/api/attendances` | `{user_id, photo?, date}` → auto set check_in_time |
| PUT | `/api/attendances/:id` | Auto set check_out_time |

### 📊 Reports (perlu token)

| Method | Path | Query Params |
|--------|------|-------------|
| GET | `/api/reports/sales` | `period` (daily/weekly/monthly/yearly), [date](file:///d:/laragon/www/belajar/bizkit/bizkit-api/controllers/user_controller.go#56-83) (YYYY-MM-DD), `stat_by` (qty/omzet) |

---

## 8. Seed Data (Data Awal)

Setiap kali server start, [SeedData()](file:///d:/laragon/www/belajar/bizkit/bizkit-api/config/database.go#55-92) di [database.go](file:///d:/laragon/www/belajar/bizkit/bizkit-api/config/database.go) akan membuat data berikut **jika belum ada**:

| Data | Nilai |
|------|-------|
| Role | `Owner` (permissions: `{"all": true}`) |
| Outlet | `Dagashi` |
| User | `ownerdemo` / `ownerdemo` (role: Owner, outlet: Dagashi) |
| Payment Methods | `Tunai`, `QRIS` |

---

## 9. Konfigurasi (.env)

```
PORT=8081                    ← Port server
DB_URL="root:@tcp(...)/bizkit..."  ← Koneksi MySQL
JWT_SECRET="super_secret_..."      ← Secret untuk JWT
```
